## Workstreams

### Innspired LoFi — 24/7 Radio Station

A continuous lofi fantasy radio stream broadcast across all major platforms. Carson's original music loops over Marwan's animation of Holdt—a steampunk Holden Caulfield writing with contented focus. The radio runs 24/7 and never stops. This is the default state of the Inn.

### E.I. Werner Live at the Inn

When E.I. Werner goes live, the Outside Inn hosts his stream. Carson's music continues at 50% volume behind gameplay. Audiences mix—radio listeners discover the host, gaming viewers discover the Inn. The Inn is always open; sometimes the innkeeper is there.

Content includes:

- Strategy games (Anno, Civilization series)
- Variety gaming
- **World of Warcraft lore series** — A custom narrative tying the Outside Inn to WoW's Goldshire history, featuring Deadkeep (a Dark Iron Dwarf Death Knight) uncovering the lost history of the original Outside Inn through the Archaeology profession

### Material Products

Collectible physical goods including posters, coasters, stickers, and vinyl records. Both stock inventory (print-on-demand) and limited-edition signed variants (1,296 numbered copies).

### Digital Products

NFT packages minted on the blockchain, including numbered loyalty badges for early Patrons and collectible art tied to album tracks. NFTs unlock exclusive online and in-person rewards.

### Community — The Innsiders

A community of supporters built through Patreon and Discord:

| Tier | Price | Rewards |
|------|-------|---------|
| **Patron** | $12/mo | Discord access, exclusive tracks, collectible stickers, Bronze badge |
| **Innsider** | $36/mo | All Patron rewards + Innsider channel, merch discount, Gold badge |

Early Patrons receive numbered NFT badges (first 1,296 Bronze, first 216 Gold).

