## How Broadcast Works

The Outside Inn operates a single 24/7 broadcast with two modes:

| Mode | What's Happening | Music |
|------|------------------|-------|
| **Radio Mode** | Holdt writing, no host | 100% volume |
| **Live Mode** | E.I. Werner streaming, hosted by the Inn | 50% background |

The Inn is always open. The innkeeper comes and goes. The music never stops.

